Package: ggfx
Title: Filters and Shaders for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Thomas Lin",
           family = "Pedersen",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "thomasp85@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5147-4711"))
Description: Provides a range of filters and shaders that can be applied to 
    layers from the 'ggplot2' package and its extensions. The filters are 
    applied at draw time and will thus respond to resizing.
